<div class="language-json" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="json" style="--shiki-light:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee;--shiki-light-bg:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code" v-pre=""><code><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666">{</span></span>
